trend that we predict will be the next sushi. Story weaves in some
of the Buford Highway culture and describes how a Mexican shrimp
cocktail is a veritable vacation in a glass. 20. Very nice art.
(Brock, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) WITH COLOR PHOTO.
</P>
