attack on the government's investigation of the sales of the San
Francisco Chronicle and the San Francisco Examiner, the Justice
Department's antitrust chief wants all critical references edited
out of the court decision. But U.S. District Judge Vaughn Walker,
in a terse reply, refused to change his ruling that was critical of
the Justice Department. By BOB EGELKO.
