<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-16 11:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3310 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-CPT-E-COMMERCE-COLUMN     08-16 1164
