 (Repeating as part of a weekly roundup of computer features)  
 &HT;    Tips for going back to school
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _
www.healthatoz.com/atoz/lifestyles/BackSchool/BSindex.asp _ Are
your kids ready to go back to school? This site is packed with
timely articles on everything from immunizations to keeping your
child's lunch safe. Also check out the top 10 signs of a good
kindergarten classroom. There's a message board for sharing
humorous back-to-school stories and other back-to-school advice.
The site is part of a larger portal, healthAtoZ.com, which includes
all manner of health news and tips for families.
</P>
<P>
   www.globalgourmet.com/food/egg/egg0997/backschool.html _ Here's
another back-to-school site to help you plan those meals on the
run, including after-school recipes such as ``Yummy Hummies''
(Middle Eastern hummus and vegetables), ``Pizza Fresca Bites'' and
``Desert Date Shake'' (a milk shake made with chopped dates). There
are also articles on the virtues of the family dinner and tips on
planning schedules to bring the whole family together at the end of
the day. The site is operated by Global Gourmet, where you'll find
innovative recipes, cooking columns and first-person essays on
food.
</P>
