economy is out to keep jobs in the United States, save sea turtles,
free Tibet, cancel the debt of poor nations, stop biotechnology,
smash sweatshops, spare the rain forests and -- depending on the
activist -- mend or mutilate the capitalist system. Will the real
revolution please stand up? Sidebars. About 1,500
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
