<P>
   EDITORS: The New York Times is planning several pages of
Democratic convention-related stories for Thursday, Aug. 17. The
New York Times News Service will file the following stories, photos
and graphics today in the ``p'' news file. This budget will be
updated by 6 p.m. ET with additional stories and details. For
repeats or information, call 888-346-9867 or 212-556-1927.
