<DOCNO> NYT20000816.0162 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-16 15:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3521 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l BC-SLOW-DOWN-LIFE-1075&AMP;a     08-16 1375
