have caused Liberace to blush, throwing beads to party-goers
(''Pearls for the girls''), Sen. John Breaux presided over perhaps
the most over-the-top party of the week, ``Mardi Gras Goes
Hollywood.'' But among those sponsoring the invitation-only event
are companies with business before committees Breaux serves on, a
pattern repeated in festivities throughout the week. (Vejnoska,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
