<SLUG> BC-SIDEBAR-FASHION-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HOW TO RULE THE SCHOOL
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Sidebar to Back-to-school fasion story) 
By BARBARA DeWITT 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   As the fall semester looms on the calendar, savvy students have
already studied up on the season's must-haves:
</P>
