</P>
<P>
   OLY-CLARK _ The womens 800-meter will be a family affair. The
three U.S. runners are all fromthe same family. Hazel Clark who won
at the U.S. trials; her sister Joetta Clark Diggs and her
sister-in-law, Jearl Miles Clark. All three are coached by J.J.
Clark, Jearl's husband, brother to the other two. (Tierney, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
