<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHIC-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times
News Service Macintosh graphics files that moved Wednesday,
08/16/00. Included is the corresponding story slug and the size.
All graphics have been posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck
Photo Database.
<TEXT>
<P>
   RUSSIA(HR)Sub damage.pdf -- 3 x 4 -- RUSSIA-SUBMARINE
